- **GNB lineage** downstream of ML Vasanthakumari not yet mapped.
- **Coimbatore N Ramaswamy** (mridangam, golden_age) — node added 2026-04-12. Trained under Palani Subrahmanya Pillai (gurukula; source: brahmanya.wordpress.com). Palani Subrahmanya Pillai not yet a node; add when Wikipedia page confirmed.
- **Lalgudi Jayaraman's guru** (Tirukodikaval Krishna Iyer) not yet a node.
- **Lakshmiratnam** (Dhanammal's third daughter) — taught both Brinda and Muktha after
